# Parallel Building:
# Supported by Sphinx 1.2.x and above
#
# Specify PARALLEL_BUILD="-j X" on the make cmdline
# If you have an 8 cpu machine, 6 might be a good number
#
# make master PARALLEL_BUILD="-j 6"
